title: Tuesday Post Show (03-08-22)

description:
Bobby starts by explaining the problem when people on the show autograph too big. We debate a couple who claims they haven’t argued in 30 years. Raymundo talks about the other job he has that we didn’t know about. He explains how he is being emasculated by a coworker. We also got into a conversation about bands that changed lead singers and had success.
